definition: class/rank/grade/equal to/same as/to wait for/to await/et cetera/and so on/et al. (and other authors)/after/as soon as/once

pinyin: bu4 deng3 bian1 san1 jiao3 xing2

sentences.english: The tolls, which include a government passage tax, varied from $4 to $30 per vehicle.
sentences.chinese: 隧道收費連政府通過稅，每程由4元至30元不等。

sentences.english: We shouldn't wait for relatives to come to our door before we take care of them.
sentences.chinese: 若論親戚之間，原該不等上門來就該有照應纔是。

sentences.english: This paper discusses a class of degenerate linear parabolic differential inequations.
sentences.chinese: 本文討論了一類拋物型變分不等式的近似收斂問題。

sentences.english: The lengths of our containers range from 10 to 40 feet.
sentences.chinese: 我們貨櫃的長度從10英尺到40英尺不等。

sentences.english: A set of inequalities which are related closely to the elliptic modular function will be set up in this paper.
sentences.chinese: 本文建立了一組與橢圓模函數密切相關的不等式。

sentences.english: What we see here does not add up to traditional Corded Ware cultural norms.
sentences.chinese: 我們在這所看到的並不等於傳統的有線窯文化規範。

sentences.english: Wang spent between half an hour and three hours on each painting.
sentences.chinese: 王月一幅畫大概要花半小時到三個小時的時間不等。

sentences.english: Students in our class range in age from 16 to 18.
sentences.chinese: 在我們班中的學生年齡從16到18不等。

sentences.english: Lateral groups of nephrons are affected more than central ones, leading to patchy atrophy with variable degrees of severity.
sentences.chinese: 受累較中央組爲重，而導致嚴重程度不等的斑狀萎縮。

sentences.english: While the price for microchip implantation Can vary, it often falls between $25 and $40.
sentences.chinese: 微芯片植入的價格不等，常在25和40美元之間。

sentences.english: Being a good friend does not mean being a doormat.
sentences.chinese: 成爲別人的好朋友並不等於可以任人踐踏。

sentences.english: The temperature deperdence of Polar Crystal Interface Polarons (PCOP) are disscussedy means of Bogolyubov inequality.
sentences.chinese: 本文利用不等式討論了界面極化子的溫度關係。

sentences.english: The radii of these regions range from 12 to 36 voxels.
sentences.chinese: 這些區域的體素數目從12個至36個不等。
學生們的答案從20克到500克不等。

sentences.english: This paper presents a new alternating direction method for a class of variational inequalities.
sentences.chinese: 該文對於一類變分不等式提出了一種新的交替方向法。

sentences.english: Authorization and access control can vary from coarse- to fine-grained.
sentences.chinese: 授權和訪問控制的粒度粗細不等。
